title: We Have Had Enough
author: wehavehadenough.dao.eth
desc: The purpose of "We Have Had Enough" is to empower service workers, advocate for their rights, foster collaboration and solidarity, promote economic justice, provide resources and education, and embrace technological innovation. Through these efforts, we strive to create a more equitable and sustainable future for service workers.

title: DevGrants DAO
author: devgrants.dao.eth
desc: A $300,000 grants program focused on growing the functionality and adoption of Aragon OSx and Aragon App. The program is targeting teams that are extending the Aragon protocol's functionality and enabling new use cases for on-chain organizations.
